brainly_data.question: How to sync info from computer to phone android
brainly_data.subject: Business

all_answers.question: How to sync info from computer to phone android
all_answers.subject: Business
all_answers.text:
♥ The best known way to do this is to connect your google account to your android.
This will work if you had this account on a previous phone because it can import your contacts, calendar dates, and more.
